THIRD-PARTY / TRADEMARK CAVEAT: the handbook names and discusses commercial cost-estimating
tools and databases (for example ACEIT, SEER-H, SEER-SEM, and PRICE TruePlanning) and cites
external standards and guides (OMB Circular A-94, the GAO Cost Estimating and Assessment
Guide GAO-09-3SP, MIL-HDBK-881C, and DoD Instruction 7041.3). Those tools, trademarks, and
standards are the property of their respective owners and are NOT placed in the public
domain by the handbook. This pack only NAMES them and synthesizes NASA's guidance about them
in original words; it reproduces none of their proprietary, trademarked, or copyrighted text.

